#### Shipping methods [/helper-shippings]

Methods for working with order shipping methods.

#### Note:
- `PUT`, `POST` will be added in the near future.
- list of available country codes for `allowedCountries` in shipping methods can be found in `GET country codes` method.
- if values of `allowedShopperGroups`, `allowedPaymentMethods` are set as an **empty array** the shipping is automaticaly available for all shopper groups and payment methods.

### GET shipping method [GET /shippings/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id: `2` (number, required) - Shipping method ID
    
+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
        
            Authorization: Basic QWxhZGRpbjpPcGVuU2VzYW1l
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Shipping)

### GET shipping methods [GET /shippings]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
        
            Authorization: Basic QWxhZGRpbjpPcGVuU2VzYW1l
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + shippingMethodList (array[Shipping])
        
### GET country codes [GET /countrycodes]

+ Request (application/json)
    + Headers
        
            Authorization: Basic QWxhZGRpbjpPcGVuU2VzYW1l
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + countryCodeList (CountryCodes)
        
