# Group Static fields

Add custom (static) fields to structures like orders, products, customers, etc.

#### Note:
- for placing a static field into **root** structure use `root` value for parent `parent`.
- for placing a static field into **sub** structure use `>` to separate array key path (for example setting parent to `address > billing` will result into adding a static value to order billing address).
- if `makeDynamic` field is set to `true` the value of the field is no longer static and can be filled with standard POST an PUT methods (these field can be placed only in root structure),
- dynamic fields are default set as a `string` (256 characters), more types (boolean, int, float) will be added in near future.

