## MetaData
+ pages: `4` (number) - Page count
+ perPage: `200` (number) - Item count per page
+ page: `1` (number) - Page number
+ list: `sku,stock,publish` (string) - List of values to return separated by comma (%2C encoded comma)
+ filterBy: `cdate` (string) - Column name to filter by (only top level values like cdate, mdate, orderStatus)
+ from: `2017-12-20 16:20:34` (string) - Available only if 'filterBy' is set to cdate or mdate
+ to: `2019-05-02 09:25:43` (string) - Available only if 'filterBy' is set to cdate or mdate
+ values: `S,D,C` (string) - Comma separated list of filtering values (%2C encoded comma)

