## Order
+ id: `101815` (number, required) - Order ID
+ cdate: `2017-12-20 16:20:34` (string) - Order creation date
+ mdate: `2019-05-02 09:25:43` (string) - Order modification date
+ note: `Hurry up with the delivery please.` (string) - Customer note
+ adminNote: `Check availability with Tim.` (string) - Order Admin note
+ orderStatus: `C` (string) - Order status (more information on 'order status' in Order Helpers->Order States)
+ currency: `EUR` (string, required) - Currency
+ currencyRate: `1` (number, required) - Currency rate
+ customerId: `223` (number, required) - Customer ID
+ invoiceNumber: `20210203` (string, required) - Invoice ID (if exists)
+ subtotalPrice: `27.30` (number) - Items sum without VAT
+ totalPrice: `36.29` (number, required) - Total order value with tax (totalPrice = subtotalPrice + tax + shipping fee + payment fee - discount)
+ tax: `6.05` (number, required) - Order tax (shipping and billing tax are included)
+ address: (object, required) - Shipping and billing address
    + billing: (BillingAddress, required) - Billing address
    + shipping: (OrderShippingAddress) - Shipping address
    + customerStaticFields: (object) - List of customer static field values (if they exist)
+ items: (array[OrderItem], required) - Order items
+ payment: (OrderPayment, required) - Payment method
+ shipping: (OrderShipping, required) - Shipping method
+ discount: (Discount) - Discount information
+ voluntaryContribution: `1.23` (number) - Voluntary contribution value
+ creditDiscount: `9.99` (number) - Credit discount value
+ cashPaymentRounding: `0.12` (number) - Cash payment Rounding 
+ ship_id: `4913355914` (string) - Shipping tracking id 

