## BillingAddress
+ name: `John` (string, required) - Name
+ surname: `Smith` (string, required) - Surname
+ email: `john.smith@gmail.com` (string, required) - Email
+ phone: `0999123456` (string, required) - Phone, a valid number must contain 16 characters or less (allowed characters are: **'0-9, +, [space], /, -, –'** of which these three: **'/, -, –'** will be converted to [space])
+ street: `Street 12` (string, required) - Street
+ city: `Bratislava` (string, required) - City
+ zip: `83104` (string, required) - Postal code
+ country: `Slovakia` (string) - Country
+ countryCode: `SVK` (string, required) - Country code
+ company: `Best John Company s.r.o.` (string) - Company name
+ ico: `123456789` (string) - Company ID
+ dic: `123456789` (string) - Company TAX ID
+ icDph: `SK123456789` (string) - Company VAT ID

