+ street: `Main street` (string, required) - Street
+ city: `Trenčín` (string) - City
+ zip: `91101` (string, required) - Postal code
+ country: `Slovakia` (string) - Country
+ countryCode: `SVK` (string, required) - Country code (complete list of country codes can be found in Order Helpers->Shipping methods->GET country codes)
+ company: (string) - Company name

