## OrderHook
+ id: `2` (number) - Hook ID
+ event: (enum, required) - Event that triggers the hook
    + `onOrderCreate` - Fires when order is created
    + `onOrderStatusChange` - Fires when order status is changed (returns only status change data)
    + `onOrderStatusChangeVerbose` - Fires when order status is changed (returns all order data)
+ active: `true` (boolean, required) - Hook state
+ url: `www.external-site.example/path/to/hook` (string, required) - Location where the data will be send
+ orderStatus: (array) - List of order states that will trigger the hook
    + `C`
    + `X`
+ orderMeaning: (array) - List of order status meanings that will trigger the hook (neutral, positive, negative)
    + `neutral`
+ cdate: `2017-12-07 16:20:34` (string) - Hook creation date
+ mdate: `2019-05-22 09:25:43` (string) - Hook modification date

## CustomerHook
+ id: `2` (number) - Hook ID
+ event: (enum, required) - Event that triggers the hook
    + `onCustomerCreate` - Fires when customer is created
    + `onCustomerChange` - Fires when customer is changed
+ active: `true` (boolean, required) - Hook state
+ url: `www.external-site.example/path/to/hook` (string, required) - Location where the data will be send
+ cdate: `2017-12-07 16:20:34` (string) - Hook creation date
+ mdate: `2019-05-22 09:25:43` (string) - Hook modification date

## OrderStatus
+ id: `2` (number) - Order status ID
+ name: `Processing order` (string, required) - Order status name
+ code: `C` (string, required) - Order status code
+ color: `ffd700` (string) - Order status color (only for GET methods)
+ meaning: `neutral` (string, required) - Order status meaning (neutral, positive, negative)
+ orderCount: `C` (string) - Number of orders with this status
+ reserved: `true` (boolean) - States with value set to true can't be removed (this value is set only from e-shop side)
+ translations: (object, required) 
    + sk: (object, required)
        + name: `Objednávka sa spracováva`

