+ limit: (object) - codes begin with 4xxx
+ 4001: `PerPage range exceeded.`
+ 4002: `Page range exceeded.`
+ 4003: `Only one price per shopper group is allowed.`
+ 4004: `Only categories with no sub-categories can be removed.`
