## InvoiceSettings
+ invoice (object)
    + documentType: (enum, required) - Type of document
        + `invoice` - Invoice
        + `creditnote` - Credit note
        + `proforma` - Advance invoice
        + `deliverynote` - Delivery note 
    + attachmentStatusList: (array, required) - order states whitelist that trigger adding selected document as email attachment when changing order status
        + P
        + C
    + iconSuffix: `F` (string) - Visual document icon modifier (shows up in shop administration) 


## OssProductRateList
+ id: `1234` (number, required) - Product ID
+ sku: `DTK1234-8` (string) - Product code (SKU)
+ countryCode: `SVK` (string, required) - Country code
+ taxRate: `23` (number, required) - Product TaxRate (value given as a percentage between 0-100)

## Article
+ id: `192` (number) - Article ID
+ title: `My Blog Post` (string) - Article title
+ perex: `Short introduction text` (string) - Article perex (intro text)
+ content: `Full article body` (string) - Article full content
+ sef: `https://www.example.com/blog/my-blog-post` (string) - Article SEF URL (absolute, including domain)
+ mainImage: `https://www.example.com/images/article/my-blog-post.jpg` (string) - Main image URL
+ authorId: `42` (number) - Author user ID
+ author: `John Doe` (string) - Author name
+ access (enum) - Article access level
    + `public` - Visible to everyone
    + `registered` - Visible to registered users only
    + `administrator` - Visible to administrators only
+ visibleFrom: `2024-01-01 00:00:00` (string, nullable) - Date from which the article is visible (null = no restriction)
+ visibleTo: `2024-12-31 23:59:59` (string, nullable) - Date until which the article is visible (null = no restriction)
+ hiddenOnDomains: (array) - List of domain hostnames on which the article is hidden
    + `shop2.example.com` (string) - Domain hostname
+ metaTitle: `My Blog Post - SEO Title` (string) - SEO meta title
+ metaDesc: `Short meta description for search engines` (string) - SEO meta description
+ metaKeywords: `blog, example, article` (string) - SEO meta keywords
+ cdate: `2024-01-15 10:00:00` (string) - Article creation date
+ mdate: `2024-03-20 14:30:00` (string) - Article modification date
+ translations: (object) - Article translations
    + cz: (object)
        + title: (string) - Article title translation
        + perex: (string) - Article perex translation
        + content: (string) - Article content translation
        + sef: (string) - Article SEF URL translation (absolute, including domain)
        + metaTitle: (string) - SEO meta title translation
        + metaDesc: (string) - SEO meta description translation
        + metaKeywords: (string) - SEO meta keywords translation

## ArticleImport
+ title: `My Blog Post` (string, required) - Article title
+ authorId: `42` (number, required) - Author user ID
+ perex: `Short introduction text` (string) - Article perex (intro text)
+ content: `Full article body` (string) - Article full content
+ sef: `my-blog-post` (string) - Article SEF slug (auto-generated from title if not provided)
+ mainImage: `https://www.example.com/images/source/my-blog-post.jpg` (string) - Main image URL (image will be downloaded by server)
+ access (enum) - Article access level
    + `public` - Visible to everyone
    + `registered` - Visible to registered users only
    + `administrator` - Visible to administrators only
+ visibleFrom: `2024-01-01 00:00:00` (string, nullable) - Date from which the article is visible
+ visibleTo: `2024-12-31 23:59:59` (string, nullable) - Date until which the article is visible
+ hiddenOnDomains: (array) - List of domain hostnames on which the article is hidden
    + `shop2.example.com` (string) - Domain hostname
+ metaTitle: `My Blog Post - SEO Title` (string) - SEO meta title
+ metaDesc: `Short meta description for search engines` (string) - SEO meta description
+ metaKeywords: `blog, example, article` (string) - SEO meta keywords
+ cdate: `2024-01-15 10:00:00` (string) - Article creation date (defaults to current date if not provided)
+ mdate: `2024-03-20 14:30:00` (string) - Article modification date (defaults to current date if not provided)
+ translations: (object) - Article translations
    + cz: (object)
        + title: (string) - Article title translation
        + perex: (string) - Article perex translation
        + content: (string) - Article content translation
        + sef: (string) - Article SEF slug translation

## ArticleUpdate
+ title: `My Blog Post` (string) - Article title
+ authorId: `42` (number) - Author user ID
+ perex: `Short introduction text` (string) - Article perex (intro text)
+ content: `Full article body` (string) - Article full content
+ sef: `my-blog-post` (string) - Article SEF slug
+ mainImage: `https://www.example.com/images/source/my-blog-post.jpg` (string) - Main image URL (image will be downloaded by server)
+ access (enum) - Article access level
    + `public` - Visible to everyone
    + `registered` - Visible to registered users only
    + `administrator` - Visible to administrators only
+ visibleFrom: `2024-01-01 00:00:00` (string, nullable) - Date from which the article is visible
+ visibleTo: `2024-12-31 23:59:59` (string, nullable) - Date until which the article is visible
+ hiddenOnDomains: (array) - List of domain hostnames on which the article is hidden
    + `shop2.example.com` (string) - Domain hostname
+ metaTitle: `My Blog Post - SEO Title` (string) - SEO meta title
+ metaDesc: `Short meta description for search engines` (string) - SEO meta description
+ metaKeywords: `blog, example, article` (string) - SEO meta keywords
+ cdate: `2024-01-15 10:00:00` (string) - Article creation date
+ mdate: `2024-03-20 14:30:00` (string) - Article modification date
+ translations: (object) - Article translations
    + cz: (object)
        + title: (string) - Article title translation
        + perex: (string) - Article perex translation
        + content: (string) - Article content translation
        + sef: (string) - Article SEF slug translation